{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hack</strong>, <strong>Slash </strong>and <strong>Carve up\u00a0</strong>waves as you journey across the Surf Realms. On your quest to unite or conquer the <strong>Coast </strong>you\u2019ll need to evolve from humble kook to certified <strong>Lord of the Waves.</strong>\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Win contests</strong>, go <strong>head to head</strong> with other surfers, <strong>earn prizes, </strong>or <strong>Free Surf</strong>. Whether you consider yourself a Star or a Soul Surfer, craft your own style on the ocean.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Coast is in Disharmony.</strong> The once sacred art of Surfriding is being sucked dry by the corporate overlords who treasure coins over stoke. As beaches are swarmed with kooks, Surf lords emerge to protect their Realms. Everywhere, things are totally un-chill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can Surfing be saved? Can balance be restored to the realm? It will take someone totally radical, but also super chill...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Be one with the wave</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use speed, style and timing to execute big tricks and combinations. Each wave is a canvas for you to carve out points. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/ezgif-6-0253146a04-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1728132367\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Soak in the Vibes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cruise through psychedelic Surf Realms with their own style and soundscape. Experience different types of waves, crowds and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069840/extras/giyof7.gif?t=1728132367\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> Journey</strong></h2><